{"tid":867830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【邊位巴打】裸男元朗街頭奔走 吊吊揈入機舖擺甫士","createTime":"2018-10-19T03:42:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T03:59:28.000Z","uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aeb5c7bcc5ff32f94feafbf11a0761d087f2c4a9","tid":867830,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181018/large/1539868078_cd8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181018%2Flarge%2F1539868078_cd8e.jpg&h=1ebe4eda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俗稱大馬路嘅青山公路元朗段，同大棠路交界一間銀行外面，噚晚8點幾有一個男人突然當街除晒衫褲鞋襪，連埋手機耳筒全部丟喺地下，佢喺條街企咗一陣，仲笑笑口咁，途人都望住佢，有人偷笑，有人攞手機出嚟影，祼男之後跑咗大概30米走入大棠路一間喺地庫嘅遊戲機中心，當時呂先生喺度打緊機，佢話在場人士見有男人冇着衫跑落嚟就起哄。<br />\n<br />\n呂先生話個裸男當時笑笑口，在場打機嘅人整蠱佢，叫佢擺吓甫士佢又照做，祼男又話自己左邊手臂有個叮噹紋身，又話自己好似蠟筆小新，總之就九唔搭八。呂先生覺得佢唔似精神有問題，懷疑佢可能有不良嗜好，過度興奮搞到自己都唔知自己做緊乜。警察接到途人報案趕到機舖，將個男人帶入洗手間，等白車到場送佢去醫院檢查。<br />\n<br />\n警方話調查後相信事件唔涉及刑事成份，35歲嘅事主之後送院。警方將案列做發現懷疑精神紊亂人士處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181018/58809027\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181018%2F58809027&d=wwoenDbXDu%2FeL7ZuvUSpHdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=9ecad4cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181018%2F58809027&h=4d5583c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181018/58809027</a><br />\n入邊有片 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5a421123c572fff40e87209d0af22bfcc866ea","tid":867830,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:44:11.000Z","msg":"找數真漢子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf01c62e38821f6ec2da3acb9c5b703795f71b1","tid":867830,"uid":89514,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:46:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f0c3fec4263644f59f538227e7464498a5a9941","tid":867830,"uid":160662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:59:28.000Z","msg":"警方話調查後相信事件唔涉及刑事成份，35歲嘅事主之後送院。警方將案列做發現懷疑精神紊亂人士處理<br />\n<br />\n個案名改左, 唔係叫傻人發現咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}